<lb n="0175b05" ed="T"/><l>纔屈於初分</l><l>餘輪狀若環</l>
<lb n="0175b06" ed="T"/><l>聖者悲願力</l><l>隨請咸來降</l>
<lb n="0175b07" ed="T"/><l>奉<note n="0175018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">現＝視【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0175018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">現【大】，視【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0175018"><lem wit="【大】">現</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">視</rdg></app>三昧耶</l><l>明契如前說</l>
<lb n="0175b08" ed="T"/><l>既呈本誓<note n="0175019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日＝已【明】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0175019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，已【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0175019"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】【乙】">已</rdg></app></l><l>決定相應故</l>
<lb n="0175b09" ed="T"/><l>次當隨力分</l><l>供養表誠心</l>
<lb n="0175b10" ed="T"/><l>閼伽香食燈</l><l>下至一花水</l>
<lb n="0175b11" ed="T"/><l>或但運心想</l><l>殊勝最難量</l>
<lb n="0175b12" ed="T"/><l>當以普通印</l><l>觀行及真言</l>
<lb n="0175b13" ed="T"/><l>有表無表俱</l><l>一切皆成就</l></lg>
<lb n="0175b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0175b1401">普通真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0175b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0175b1501" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0175020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（娜莫…喃引））十一字＝（（曩莫薩嚩怛他蘖帝驃尾濕嚩目契弊））十五字【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0175020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（娜莫…喃引）十一字【大】，曩莫薩嚩怛他蘖帝驃尾濕嚩目契弊【甲】【乙】</note><app cb:word-count="11" n="0175020"><lem wit="【大】">娜莫三<note n="0175021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）細註【明】</note><note n="0175021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，去(聲)【明】</note><app n="0175021"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">去</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">去聲</note></rdg></app>滿多母馱<note place="inline">引</note>喃<note n="0175022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（一）細註【明】＊</note><note n="0175022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，引(一)【明】＊</note><app n="0175022"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">引一</note></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">曩莫薩嚩怛他蘖帝驃尾濕嚩目契弊</rdg></app>薩嚩他<note place="inline">去聲引</note>欠
